headline: Sip at Sea: A Princess Cruises Cocktail Collection by Global Mixologist Rob Floyd Now Available on Amazon

headline: Holland America Line to Celebrate Nearly 80 Years of Alaska Exploration with Debut Float in the 2025 Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade®
summary: Holland America Line is bringing the splendors of Alaska to New York City next month with its debut float in the 99th Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade® on Thursday, Nov. 27, 2025. Ahead of the cruise line's 80th anniversary of exploring the Great Land, the float will evoke the state's majestic landscapes and indomitable spirit through artistry and dynamic design.
